Package: com.nextsolution.dailyledger.smsimport
Name: Daily Ledger SMS Import
Version: 1.1.2
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64e
Description: Automatically imports QAR bank SMS containing the exact configured marker, including **6760, into a selected Daily Ledger account. Includes RootHide container entitlements, attributed-message decoding, recent-message recovery, importer status, and one vibration after a successful import. Requires RootHide Bootstrap 2.0 or later and Daily Ledger 1.3.2 or later.
Maintainer: NextSolution
Author: NextSolution
Section: Utilities
Priority: optional
